metadata.name: Ghost Rider
metadata.description:
A different city, a moodier one; rushing to capture the moment while the rain is still pouring…  
A biker appears like he escaped from a detention center but he’s obeying the law because he doesn’t want to draw attention. All he wants is to escape forever, to become a ghost, so he endures whatever life throws at him!


3901 × 5852
